metadata.name: Framed
metadata.description: Discko bay, one of the most amazing places I have visited. I was fortunate to be able to visit this Unesco World Heritage sites last year September. What an experience it was so sail around these beautiful icebergs. We were very lucky with the weather that day and also we found a one of a kind icberg. Our second vessel sailed around the icerberg so that we could get this unique shot.
